Multi-LoRA Serving Architecture with vLLM. Single Base Model (Llama 70B) in VRAM. Multiple LoRA Adapters (SQL, Email, Code, Translation) as small overlay matrices. Request Router selects adapter by model name header. Dynamic adapter loading, no model reload. Memory: Base 140GB + 4 Adapters ~32MB total. Throughput: 1000 req/s shared base. German labels, server architecture diagram.